snippet.title: Please Insert Disc | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
From the creators of Home Safety Hotline, Please Insert Disc is an upcoming puzzle horror game set in 2002 about navigating the underbelly of your game console to restore its functionality - but waking something in the process. 💿

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2855360/Please_Insert_Disc
